method2:
To identify enriched transcription factor binding, the top 500 overexpressed or underexpressed genes 
within a condition were uploaded to the Enrichr web tool26,27,28 to quantify enrichment for ENCODE and 
ChEA consensus transcription factor targets. We visualized gene expression patterns using pheatmap() 
in R or using GraphPad Prism. Analyses were conducted using R software (v.4.2.2).
Ref: 
NADPH-producing enzymes restrict the formation of pancreatic precancerous lesions. Nat Metab. 2026. pmid: 41922743
